    </input>
  </session>

  If you have trouble on <shell|brew link qt --force> and <shell|brew unlink
  qt>. Make sure that you have installed Qt before using homebrew:

  <\session|shell|default>
    <\input>
      Shell]\ 
    <|input>
      brew install qt
    </input>
  </session>

